            </b>11-14 July 2011 - PRAGUE<br>
            This is the first call for the 8th EFITA conference that will b=
e held=20
            from 11th to 14th July 2011 at the campus site of the Czech Uni=
versity=20
            of Life Sciences Prague, in a beautiful landlocked country in t=
he=20
            heart of Europe, in the Czech Republic. This letter is to brief=
