            This conference is co-organized with the 8th ECPA, the 5th ECPL=
F conferences=20
            as there is an established tradition of bringing EFITA, ECPA an=
d ECPLF=20
            together.<br>
            &gt;&gt;&gt; The main topics are as follows:<br>
            - Food quality<br>
            - SDI for Agriculture and Food industry<br>
            - Sensor technologies<br>
            - Future trends<br>
            - ICT Adoption<br>
            - Knowledge Management<br>
            - e-business<br>
            - Standardisation and Interoperability<br>
            - Rural development<br>
            - Nature protection<br>
