ominican=20
            Republic, dedicated to appropriate technologies and methodologi=
es=20
            for sustainable development. The organisation combines ICTs, wo=
men=B4s=20
            empowerment and agro-processing in their work to assist rural c=
ooperatives.=20
            Taig=FCey focuses on community projects that involve women and =
farmers=20
            from La Ci=E9naga, a small rural community in the Southwest of =
the Dominican=20
            Republic.<br>
            See: <a
href=3D"http://www.taiguey.org" target=3D"_blank">http:/www.taiguey.org</a>=
